            . I took the prisoner; I found nothing on her - there were two more girls who she wanted me to take.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I found the hat four doors from the prosecutor's.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 18.</p>
